lastCommitMessage: Enhance product checkout components with UI improvements and functionality updates
- Updated the layout of the order remark and payment details sections to include icons and improved styling for better user experience.
- Increased the maximum lines for the remark input field and adjusted its placeholder text for clarity.
- Enhanced the display of selected specifications with improved styling and layout.
- Refactored the shipping selector and address components to streamline address management and improve visual consistency.
- Introduced loading states for better user feedback during data fetching processes in the product purchase confirmation page.
